          <p>Here’s an example to help illustrate the importance of win:win: Imagine you are driving along in your car on a wild, stormy night. You drive by a bus stop and you see three people waiting for the bus… now click on the video below to find out the solution:
          </p>
            <video width="100%" controls poster="video/poster.png">
