        <div class="quote">
          <img src="images/quote-grey.png" class="img-responsive quoteMarks">
            <em>A business exists in an eco-system and has stakeholders (customers, suppliers, shareholders). For a business to run smoothly, it needs to keep all its stakeholders happy. Businesses need to revisit their model at regular intervals in order to create a continuous win-win situation for everyone involved.
            </em>
        </div>
        <div class="name">
          <h5>Graduate innovator</h5>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

